Tyrael was hit by the shots from Proto, but went on without caring 
about it. He barely escaped Skulletron's missile, but managed it 
nonetheless.

He opened a commline to the newcomers, deciding any help was better 
than a stand alone at that time.

Tyrael: I am Major Tyrael and I am in charge. Report your names, 
please.

The hits he had landed on Skulletron were a good start, and he 
intended to go on. However, he saw the falling pod.

Tyrael: Womanbot, hold out. Get to that pod and secure it for the 
Tripredacus! Here, insert that in it!

He throws a Tripredacus programming chip at her. He looked at the 
shield's gauge and saw it had dropped yet again... 80 - no - 79%, and 
still falling. He slashed twice again at Skulletron and, turning back 
a little, sent a massive light bolt at Proto.

Even before he had started to fire on him, Vlad realized Waspinator 
had been hit hard. He was not an immediate threat.

Vlad: Greetings, Major Tyrael. I am Khan Vladimir Ward of Clan Wolf. I 
will assist your Tripredacus.

He switched targets to Inferno and launched all mini-missiles on the 
ant.
